пляжі;</span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span class="a-libMegablockContentClass" id="Price_inc_span"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left" id="price_inc_exc_edit_inc_3081_span">користування парасольками на пляжі (1 парасолька на 4 особи);</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span class="a-libMegablockContentClass" id="Price_inc_span"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left" id="price_inc_exc_edit_inc_3082_span">користування інфраструктурою комплексу, басейн, спортивний інвентар;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span class="a-libMegablockContentClass" id="Price_inc_span"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left" id="price_inc_exc_edit_inc_3083_span">цілодобова охорона;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span class="a-libMegablockContentClass" id="Price_inc_span"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left" id="price_inc_exc_edit_inc_3084_span">цілодобовий медпункт;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span class="a-libMegablockContentClass" id="Price_inc_span"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left"><span align="left">один керівник на 15 дітей.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td colspan="2">\n			<p><b><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><font color="#990000"><img align="absmiddle" height="26" src="http://www.algol.com.ua/tours/i/icons/checkbox_2.gif" wid